{{`select user_id
, max_by(email, length(product_images)) email 
, max_by(nickname, length(product_images)) nickname 
, max_by(country, length(product_images)) country 
, max_by(subs_type, length(product_images))
, max_by(region, length(product_images)) region
, max_by(city, length(product_images)) city   
, max_by(product_link, length(product_images)) product_link   
, max_by(product_images, length(product_images)) product_images   
, max_by(product_description, length(product_images)) product_description   
, max_by(product_name, length(product_images)) product_name   
, max_by(gmt_create,length(product_images)) gmt_create
from marketing.link_scraper_user
group by user_id`}}
